BAT MASTERSON 

2x73. Blood on the Money 6/23/1960
Before Bat&#039;s partner in a casino venture is dies, he asks Masterson to deliver his share of the money to his brother on the Mexican border. Bat learns that the man is rumored to lead a gang of rustlers.

2x74. Barbary Castle  6/30/1960
An old sea captain has dismantled his clan&#039;s Scottish castle and is rebuilding it in San Francisco. The company stockholder&#039;s serve him with a restraining order, claiming he&#039;s wasting the business&#039; assets constructing such an extravagant building.
    Guest star: Jay Novello (Captain MacLeod), Gloria Talbott (Mary), Stuart Bradley (Tracy Crow)
